(64,'sowjanya-msl-593000179','Fitness Tracking Application',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Developed an application on fitness track of the customer performing his/her workout each day. It has register/login pages, customer can view what kinds of workouts the app offers, learn about them and proceed performing the same. Also, this has a history section to track their progress. We have used Java and firebase authentication technique to maintain the integrity of the data of each customer.',NULL),
