(58,'reidhoffman','Chair, Board of Directors','1','6','2016',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Opportunity@Work is a nonprofit social enterprise dedicated to re-wiring the U.S. labor market through innovative technology and education financing. Opportunity@Work has launched TechHire.Careers, a new kind of recruiting platform built to help employers fill entry-level tech positions with talented individuals from diverse backgrounds. \n\nBy breaking down systemic barriers facing job seekers who come from nontraditional backgrounds, Opportunity@Work will enable millions of Americans to find good jobs and generate more than $20 billion in additional annual earnings for the U.S. labor market.','Opportunity@Work'),
